text: Þis sindon þa landgemæro to Duclingtune XIIII hida & þa ealdan cyricean æt æstlea & þær to XL æcera.
And byrnan lea eal into Duclingtune.
Ærest of duclingtune on weric &lang wenrices on þone byge of þam byge on þa ealdan lace.
Andlang lace on þa norð ea &lang streames on folgor hyrste neoþewearde þonon on þa ealdan dic.
Andlang dic<../images/tbar.gif>suð eft on wænric up ongean stream on þone ealdan ford.
Of þone forda up on þa Riþe an furlang wið svþan þa cyrican &lang Riþe on þa wurtwalan<../images/tbar.gif>ut þurh þone hagan on burh dic ufeuuearde.
Of þære dic on þa ealdan Rode of þære rode on scottes healh of þam heale on uuenburge byrgge of þæra brucge on þa dic.
Andlang dices on east hæma gemære on þone bige to þan heafdan on gate þyrnan.
Of þære þyrnan on blace þyrnan on þa dic of þære þyrnan to uurt walan to þan furan &lang fura on þa ealdan dic to þan ellere &lang dices to þan oþerne ellene.
Of þan ellene to þære apoldre ðanon to æglesuullan broce up ongean stream on stanford of þan forda on fugelslæd of þam slæde on coluullan broc &lang broces on swyllan healas.
Of þan healan on hastinges lace &lang lace on þone eastream.
And twegan hammas æt loppede þorne hyrað in to Duclingdune.
